QuestData.Title: Mung-Mung's Vote I: A Hozen's Problem
QuestData.Description: I've been thinkin' about how to get into the Tiller's good graces, $n.$B$BNow, the Tiller's Union accepts new farmers each year, and there are five members on the voting council.$B$BWe already got Gina's vote, but we'll have to prove ourselves to the other four members of their board.$B$BWhy don't you go over and say hello to Mung-Mung? He works with Mr. Mudclaw out on the Mudclaw's farm to the northwest.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak to Mung-Mung at Haohan Mudclaw's House in the Valley of the Four Winds.
